Package: wcc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libcapstone3, libelf1, libreadline7, libgsl2
Description: WCC is a collection of tools to manipulate binaries and shared objects
 WCC permits one to manipulate binaries and shared liraries to reuse
 their API into an external usage, as a relocatable object that
 can be linked to a new project, or through an interpreter (wsh)
 to execute internal API directly.

Package: wcc-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: The WCC complete internal documentation and Howtos
 All documentations including Doxygen output and various Howtos on how
 to use the Witchcraft Compiler Collection.
 This documentation also include various examples.


